{"id": 1152, "genre": 1001, "title": "工作之后，你觉得这份工作和你之前对它的预想有啥区别？", "description": "如同买家秀和卖家图的对比，可是没有运费险。（题图来自：Christopher Silas Neal）", "record_count": 2969, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160807165011CYbOaRUQ59HFnGBu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-18T03:10:38Z", "options": [{"id": 108544, "content": "起码不要每天都去套路客户，我只想认认真真做好一个客户的方案设计", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667615}, {"id": 108545, "content": "好人有好报？呵呵。斗米恩升米仇！", "image": "img/option/option_pic/201608181222243CG1fiylFHeN4nXzr.jpg", "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397696}, {"id": 108546, "content": "恩？我就做这么一点事情？", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584387}, {"id": 108547, "content": "工作太无聊，没有干劲，换家公司还一样，老司机们还一口一个不要躁动的给人灌鸡汤…", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709676}, {"id": 108803, "content": "最可怕的是面对各种不专业", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654398}, {"id": 108548, "content": "说多了都是泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720999}, {"id": 108804, "content": "工作之后才发现自己在很多事情上都是无力的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722973}, {"id": 108549, "content": "工作以后，整个人越来越不好了...", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721000}, {"id": 110597, "content": "办公室政治太可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679121}, {"id": 108550, "content": "看著都好友善，哪知把最髒最累的活丟給你，還要道一句謝謝！", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720997}, {"id": 137479, "content": "谁认真工作谁傻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689742}, {"id": 108551, "content": "把肉体出卖了，将灵魂封藏了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720992}, {"id": 108553, "content": "点亮心中噩梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567823}, {"id": 108809, "content": "无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670919}, {"id": 108554, "content": "我以为身边会有各种大牛，结果只有牛,只会耕地", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720044}, {"id": 108555, "content": "觉得自己就是个工具啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719079}, {"id": 108556, "content": "上一份工作真像躺着赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689378}, {"id": 115724, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈咕咚咕咚的嘎嘎嘎嘎好好的合法化伏本许多斑斑点点吧吧的活动不断不断不断不断不断不断斑斑点点并不代表蛇年大吉姬东好多好多好多好多话哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈咕咚咕咚的嘎嘎嘎嘎好好的合法化伏本许多斑斑点点吧吧的活动不断不断不断不断哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450371}, {"id": 108557, "content": "上面的人永远看不到你的努力\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 639557}, {"id": 109069, "content": "工作以后对梦想与现实理解的更好了，感觉电影都是骗子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 426504}, {"id": 108558, "content": "creative和Ctrl+c的区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721068}, {"id": 108559, "content": "每天都觉得自己特牛逼，但却总被别人的消极情绪污染，推动不了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149495}, {"id": 108561, "content": "开始思考如何掌握一门技术，只用搞好自己不用整其他没用的那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638163}, {"id": 108817, "content": "一开始觉得公司的项目很有前景，抱有很大的期待。然后并不是那样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723030}, {"id": 108562, "content": "老板有脾气随便发。我却只能往肚吞。这是一个不讲理的世界。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338358}, {"id": 108563, "content": "换过几次工作后，期待值与实际值误差变小", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709777}, {"id": 108564, "content": "会装X的傻X都不会混得太差。哪怕是在互联网公司。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 6350}, {"id": 108565, "content": "主动加班和被动加工作量的区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518624}, {"id": 108566, "content": "区别大了去了。。。没有一个和我预想的符合??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696155}, {"id": 108567, "content": "同事人都很好 很喜欢 何其有幸", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633090}, {"id": 108568, "content": "想要做好一件事情往往用的都不是最快的办法，而是最平衡所有人利益的办法，相应的就是牺牲时间。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471092}, {"id": 108569, "content": "勾心斗角太多，为了达到目的什么都干，我也是服了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684162}, {"id": 110617, "content": "想着用聪明才智赚钱，没想到最后是拿命换。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684271}, {"id": 108570, "content": "把无聊藏进心底，还是得工作~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694548}, {"id": 108571, "content": "没想到这么多sb", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657898}, {"id": 108572, "content": "理想很丰满，现实很骨感！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671181}, {"id": 108573, "content": "加强学习潮汕话", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699653}, {"id": 108574, "content": "曾经毕业后工作两年满满的都是抱怨！因公调去其他项目，意外被客户大加赞赏！恍然大悟，磨练皆是福缘，厚积而薄发。现在每次跳槽都先挖掘新公司的优点和资源，世界从此不同！", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575094}, {"id": 108575, "content": "原来跟人事谈薪资的自己就是一只弱鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721165}, {"id": 108576, "content": "以为工资还可以 七七八八一扣完 到手原来很不可以?", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 516685}, {"id": 108577, "content": "SEX?NO.LIFE FUCKS ME EVERYDAY", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721172}, {"id": 108578, "content": "工作之后作息时间都正常了，和想象中不一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721153}, {"id": 108579, "content": "你那别人当朋友 朋友踩着你的尸体往上爬", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721177}, {"id": 108580, "content": "我的理想有多大，要看岗位给我的空间有多大", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721179}, {"id": 108581, "content": "我的时间都被透支了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721191}, {"id": 108582, "content": "老板总是物尽其用 总是会有你自己都想象不出的功能让你惊讶 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721181}, {"id": 108583, "content": "做的不是工作，处的是关系。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721203}, {"id": 108584, "content": "为了这个工作推掉了另一个工作，结果发现那个工作正在真正的盈利", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713644}, {"id": 108840, "content": "一份不如一份好，开始思考自己到底适合做什么……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721575}, {"id": 108585, "content": "害怕衰老", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672482}]}